{"title":"Beat the rush and save $140 on the Apple Watch Series 6 with LTE","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/357285/beat-the-rush-and-save-140-on-the-apple-watch-series-6-with-lte.html","date":1631292930000,"content":"<div>\n<section><div></div></section><p>There may be <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/348953/2021-apple-watch-series-7-design-display-features-release.html\">a new Apple Watch on the way</a> in just a few days, but you can get a great one at a great price right now. Amazon is selling the <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/product/B08J5FXJN7,B08J5FXJN6,B08J5RBMRN,B08J5P53JK?tag=macworld05-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://www.macworld.com/feed\">Red 40mm Series 6 with GPS and Cellular for $359</a>, good for $140 off the MSRP, and the best price we’ve ever seen.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Apple Watch Series 6 is Apple’s flagship wearable, with an always-on display and an array of sensors and features, including blood-oxygen, ECG, and heart rate. With an LTE connection, you won’t need to keep your phone around and you’ll still be able to make calls, send texts, and get app updates. <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/234682/apple-watch-series-6-review.html\">In our review</a>, we wrote that “you’re not going to find another smartwatch that’s as fast, featured, fashionable, or just plain fun.”</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So while you can wait for the <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/348953/2021-apple-watch-series-7-design-display-features-release.html\">Apple Watch Series 7</a>, which could bring better battery life and a slightly larger display, we think you’ll be very happy with the Series 6, especially at this price. </p>\n\n\n\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t<h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</h4>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Apple Watch Series 6</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://images.idgesg.net/images/article/2020/09/apple-watch-series-